    "- **Sensitivity analysis** to understand parameter impact\n",
    "- **Benchmark** for evaluating heuristic and metaheuristic methods\n",
    "\n",
    "### Pros / Cons vs other approaches\n",
    "**Pros:**\n",
    "- Guaranteed optimal solution (for small problems)\n",
    "- Transparent decision-making process\n",
    "- Clear mathematical formulation\n",
    "- Easy to understand and explain\n",
    "\n",
    "**Cons:**\n",
    "- Limited scalability for larger problems\n",
    "- Requires complete information\n",
    "- Computationally expensive for many carriers/lane combinations\n",
    "- Cannot handle uncertainty or dynamic changes\n",
    "\n",
    "### When to use this Tier\n",
    "- **Small-scale problems** with few carriers and lanes\n",
    "- **Strategic decisions** where optimality is critical\n",
    "- Benchmark development for evaluating other methods\n",
